\f1\b 5-Day AI Agents: Intensive Vibe Coding Course with Google
\f0\b0 . You can find the additional codelabs and resources available on the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/5-day-ai-agents-intensive-vibecoding-course-with-google"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 event site}}.\
